Home Baked Orange/Lemon 🍋pound cake. 
Second attempt. 
This time managed to make the glaze over the cake, however the texture can still be improve :) .
Supposed to be Orange 🍊 pound cake, but it turned out to be more like Lemon 🍋pound cake 😂. .
Thank you @shirine.kho @kevin.voon for being my guinea pig and advice 🙏🏻. .
